snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Amber Heard hand in hand...
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard showed plenty of affection as they attended the Art of Elysium charity gala hand-in-hand.  Depp appeared brooding while his fiance was in good spirits.
